commit.message:
implement use of nanoVG when rendering with an active mask

This significally reduces the amount of AsyncDrawJobs when rendering
with an active mask.
rework rendering of enhanced blend modes
fix refcounting in Array.splice

rework DisplayObject invalidation handling

This removes calls to getMatrix() and access to the dynamicDisplayList
of DisplayObjectContainers from inside the rendering thread.
This is the first step to remove all access to the DisplayList from the
rendering thread.
[AVM1] handle corner cases for ActionStringExtract

[AVM1] fix order of function name lookup for ActionCallFunction

this re-enables moving around in the Fancy Pants Adventure title screen

[DisplayObjectContainer] only remember last frame if it was placed
before the next frame
[DisplayObject] fix refcounting in AVM1GetClipFromPath

Revert "[AVM1] fix refcounting on ActionGetProperty/ActionSetProperty"

This reverts commit 8d5c2d1c7bc9b7e707e38c49fb62575e3c1a34cf.
[AVM1] fix refcounting on ActionGetProperty/ActionSetProperty

fix possible crash on SoundStreamHeadTag destruction

don't delete the MemoryStreamCache here
as that is properly handled through reset()

really solve reusing of DisplayObjects through tags

this takes a better and simpler approach by just keeping a list
of the children  of the last declared frame and looking in this list
when executing PlaceObject tags

[AVM1] make avm1 variable name lowercase in ActionSetMember

fixes display of coin count in supermario63 start screen
another try to fix reusing of DisplayObjects through tags
check EventDispatcher for garbage collection after event is handled

ensure that the root movie is added to stage after the constructor of
the builtin class was called.

This fixes the rendering of the startup sequence in BejeweledTwist
ignore QtCreator generated files

[DisplayObjectContainer] reset skipFrame for everything but MovieClips

fixes playing of ArmorGames logo on NeonRider
another fix for reusing of DisplayObjects through tags
fix reusing of DisplayObjects through tags
[TokenContainer] Add window offset when not rendering filters

improved reusing of DisplayObjects through tags

this improves moving backwads in the timeline
and removes an ugly hack

[PlaceObject2Tag] reset properties of reused DisplayObjects

fixes #1010
ensure DisplayObjects with ClipDepth are not rendered outside of mask

[DisplayObjectContainer] update legacy children after displaylist
changed

fixes several rendering issues in TrainMania
fix crash introdced in last commit
[Graphics] implement readGraphicsData

[MovieClip] avoid duplicate advance in AVM1 after constructionComplete

fixes display of "play now" button in "Fancy Pants Adventure: World 3"

cleanup rendering by removing a lot of unneccessary stuff

this removes multiple entries in IDrawable that are not needed for the
new rendering pipeline

[global] Initial work on putting interfaces in separate headers

Just like the previous commit, this also helps reduce partial rebuild
times.

Maybe, at some point, we can figure out how to auto generate these.
